name: Ptsans-npm-webfont
body:
## PTsans webfont package

### Usage

in module
```
import 'ptsans-npm-webfont';
```

in style

```
body {
  font-family: 'PT Sans', sans-serif;
}
```

Webpack dependencies:
- style-loader
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
